Shielded USDC
=============

This project is an independent, clean-room ERC-20 (USDC) adaptation of a
Tornado-Cash-style fixed-denomination privacy protocol. It deliberately does NOT
reuse the name, branding, logo, or marketing copy of any upstream project.

