Trusted setup
-------------

The proving key (withdraw_final.zkey) and Verifier.sol originate from a Groth16
trusted setup that the maintainers of THIS repository did not perform. They are
treated as inherited and unverified. Re-run the Phase-2 ceremony and regenerate
these artifacts before any production use. See README "Trusted-setup / artifact
assumptions".
